ISLAMABAD, Aug 21 (APP): Muttahida Qaumi Movement (MQM) central leader and joint in-charge of inter-provincial organisational committee Zahid Malik has welcomed the decision of Punjab Chief Minister Maryam Nawaz to reduce electricity bills.
In a statement, Malik said by taking this step, Ms Nawaz had left all the other provinces behind,Â  said in a Press Release issued here on Wednesday.
